{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866452692,"sessionID":"ses_2861cb645ffenLKX5dolBFx5a7","part":{"id":"prt_d79e38fa0001KkBkxV1eg2ihrR","messageID":"msg_d79e374010011My73ctzL7SvYv","sessionID":"ses_2861cb645ffenLKX5dolBFx5a7","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-bb0df173f7c94d8585fc3b0e777dc0a2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-018 |\n8: | Module | pkg/agentd |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 实现一个轻量级 Kubernetes 控制器，用于自动清理空闲超时的 `Sandbox` 自定义资源。\n17: \n18: **Current State**: 当前项目中，`pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 实现了基于轮询的垃圾回收机制，通过定期扫描检查 Sandbox 的空闲状态。这种方式存在延迟较高、资源利用率不优的问题。\n19: \n20: **Target State**: 引入 `pkg/agentd` 模块，使用 controller-runtime 的 Reconciler 模式，基于事件驱动的空闲清理。控制器将：\n21: 1. 监听 `Sandbox` CR 的创建/更新事件\n22: 2. 读取 `last-activity-time` annotation 判断空闲状态\n23: 3. 计算 15 分钟空闲阈值，到期自动删除资源\n24: 4. 使用 RequeueAfter 实现精确的延迟删除调度\n25: \n26: ---\n27: \n28: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n29: \n30: ### 2.1 In Scope\n31: \n32: | Deliverable | Description |\n33: |-------------|-------------|\n34: | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | Reconciler 实现，包含空闲检测与删除逻辑 |\n35: | `cmd/agentd/main.go` | 独立二进制入口，启动 controller-runtime manager |\n36: | Scheme 注册 | 注册 core Kubernetes types + `sandboxv1alpha1` |\n37: | 单元测试 | Reconciler 核心逻辑测试 |\n38: \n39: ### Implementation Details\n40: \n41: **核心常量**:\n42: ```go\n43: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n44: ```\n45: \n46: **Annotation Key**: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` = `\"last-activity-time\"`\n47: \n48: **Reconcile 算法**:\n49: 1. 获取 Sandbox CR\n50: 2. 解析 `last-activity-time` annotation (RFC3339 格式)\n51: 3. 计算 `expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min`\n52: 4. 若 `now.After(expirationTime)` → 删除 Sandbox\n53: 5. 否则 → `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`\n54: \n55: **Watch 资源**:\n56: | API group | Version | Kind |\n57: |-----------|---------|------|\n58: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` |\n59: \n60: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n61: \n62: - AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CR 控制器 (由 AR-007 处理)\n63: - Webhook (Validating/Mutating)\n64: - Metrics 暴露\n65: - 领导选举 (单实例部署)\n66: - 现有 `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 的重构或移除\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n71: \n72: ### 3.1 新增文件\n73: \n74: ```\n75: pkg/agentd/\n76: └── reconciler.go           # Reconciler 结构体与 Reconcile 方法\n77: \n78: cmd/agentd/\n79: └── main.go                 # 独立二进制入口\n80: ```\n81: \n82: ### 3.2 Upstream Dependencies\n83: \n84: | Dependency | Version | Impact |\n85: |------------|---------|--------|\n86: | `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.19.0 | 核心框架 |\n87: | `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | - | Sandbox CRD 类型 |\n88: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.31.0 | API 错误处理、runtime.Scheme |\n89: | `k8s.io/client-go` | v0.31.0 | Kubernetes 客户端 |\n90: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` | - | Annotation 常量 |\n91: \n92: ### 3.3 Downstream Consumers\n93: \n94: | Consumer | Method Usage |\n95: |----------|--------------|\n96: | 运维部署 | 部署 `agentd` 作为独立 DaemonSet/Deployment |\n97: | Sandbox 资源管理 | 自动清理空闲资源，释放集群资源 |\n98: \n99: ### 3.4 Breaking Change Considerations\n100: \n101: 无破坏性变更。这是新增模块，不影响现有功能。\n102: \n103: ### 3.5 Compatibility Notes\n104: \n105: - 与现有 `workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 功能重叠，但互不干扰\n106: - `agentd` 可作为 garbage_collector 的补充或替代部署\n107: - Annotation key 需与 workloadmanager 保持一致 (`last-activity-time`)\n108: \n109: ---\n110: \n111: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n112: \n113: ### Alternative 1: controller-runtime Reconciler (推荐)\n114: \n115: **Approach**: 使用 sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime 的 Reconciler 模式，监听 Sandbox CR 变更。\n116: \n117: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n118: |--------|------------|\n119: | Pros | 事件驱动、精确调度 (RequeueAfter)、代码简洁、与 K8s 生态兼容 |\n120: | Cons | 需要独立进程运行、依赖 controller-runtime 框架 |\n121: \n122: **Implementation**:\n123: ```go\n124: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n125:     sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}\n126:     if err := r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox); err != nil {\n127:         return ctrl.Result{}, client.IgnoreNotFound(err)\n128:     }\n129:     \n130:     lastActivityStr := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n131:     if lastActivityStr == \"\" {\n132:         return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n133:     }\n134:     \n135:     lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)\n136:     if err != nil {\n137:         return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err\n138:     }\n139:     \n140:     expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n141:     if time.Now().After(expirationTime) {\n142:         return ctrl.Result{}, client.IgnoreNotFound(r.Delete(ctx, sandbox))\n143:     }\n144:     \n145:     return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil\n146: }\n147: ```\n148: \n149: ### Alternative 2: 现有轮询式 GC\n150: \n151: **Approach**: 复用 `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 的轮询模式。\n152: \n153: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n154: |--------|------------|\n155: | Pros | 无需新增进程、代码已存在 |\n156: | Cons | 延迟高 (轮询间隔)、资源浪费、无法精确调度 |\n157: \n158: **Decision**: 选择 **Alternative 1 (controller-runtime Reconciler)**\n159: \n160: 理由:\n161: 1. 精确调度：使用 `RequeueAfter` 在准确的过期时间触发删除\n162: 2. 资源高效：事件驱动，无空转轮询\n163: 3. 可扩展：未来可轻松添加更多控制器逻辑\n164: 4. 与 AR-007 架构一致\n165: \n166: ### Alternative 3: CronJob 定时任务\n167: \n168: **Approach**: 使用 Kubernetes CronJob 定期扫描删除空闲 Sandbox。\n169: \n170: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n171: |--------|------------|\n172: | Pros | 无需常驻进程、部署简单 |\n173: | Cons | 延迟高 (Cron 间隔)、无法精确调度、需额外 RBAC 配置 |\n174: \n175: ---\n176: \n177: ## 5. Risks\n178: \n179: | Risk | Mitigation |\n180: |------|------------|\n181: | 误删活跃 Sandbox | 解析失败时 Requeue 30s 重试，不直接删除 |\n182: | 时钟偏移导致提前/延迟删除 | 使用 server-side timestamp 或考虑 toleration |\n183: | annotation 缺失导致资源泄漏 | 由 workloadmanager 创建时保证 annotation 存在 |\n184: | 删除失败重试风暴 | controller-runtime 内置 exponential backoff |\n185: \n186: ---\n187: \n188: ## 6. Implementation Checklist\n189: \n190: 1. **Phase 1: 搭建框架**\n191:    - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`，定义 Reconciler 结构体\n192:    - [ ] 创建 `cmd/agentd/main.go`，启动 manager\n193:    - [ ] 注册 Scheme (core + sandboxv1alpha1)\n194: \n195: 2. **Phase 2: 实现 Reconcile 逻辑**\n196:    - [ ] 实现 annotation 解析与时间计算\n197:    - [ ] 实现删除逻辑与错误处理\n198:    - [ ] 实现 RequeueAfter 调度\n199: \n200: 3. **Phase 3: 测试**\n201:    - [ ] 单元测试：解析成功/失败场景\n202:    - [ ] 单元测试：过期/未过期场景\n203:    - [ ] 单元测试：Get/Delete 错误处理\n204: \n205: 4. **Phase 4: 部署配置**\n206:    - [ ] 编写 Deployment/DaemonSet manifest\n207:    - [ ] 配置 RBAC (Sandbox CRUD 权限)\n208: \n209: ---\n210: \n211: ## 7. References\n212: \n213: - AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n214: - `idle-cleanup/design.md`: 详细设计文档\n215: - `idle-cleanup/spec.md`: 需求规格\n216: - controller-runtime: https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\n217: - `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go`: Annotation 常量定义\n218: - `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go`: 现有 GC 实现参考\n\n(End of file - total 218 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-018 |\n| Module | pkg/agentd |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n实现一个轻量级 Kubernetes 控制器，用于自动清理空闲超时的 `Sandbox` 自定义资源。\n\n**Current State**: 当前项目中，`pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 实现了基于轮询的垃圾回收机制，通过定期扫描检查 Sandbox 的空闲状态。这种方式存在延迟较高、资源利用率不优的问题。\n\n**Target State**: 引入 `pkg/agentd` 模块，使用 controller-runtime 的 Reconciler 模式，基于事件驱动的空闲清理。控制器将：","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775866452663,"end":1775866452690}}}}
